</table>
    
  </li>
  
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
   Test your custom domain works by visiting <code>/example</code>!<span class="no-mobile"><br>You'll still need to visit 0tr.me to shorten URLs, but now you can share links with your own domain.</span>

  </li>
</ol>
